      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4 animate-slide-up">
          Oferuję <span class="font-bold text-blue-700 relative group inline-block">kompleksowe rozwiązania
            <span class="absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-0 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-indigo-400 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500 ease-out"></span>
          </span> w zakresie tworzenia nowoczesnych stron internetowych
        </p>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed animate-slide-up animation-delay-200">
